>\n<br />\n我又唔覺得風扇啲風力會勁到令你呼唔到氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e7a5f7cc209b0b37dc4eaa9b0797ae89b412c2","tid":295713,"uid":4519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T10:58:00.000Z","msg":"除左過熱都無乜原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"479f343a60ac953030026f9d476c3a02706b53e5","tid":295713,"uid":38691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T11:03:40.000Z","msg":"因為佢地思想仲停留係以前 過你老母熱咩 把風扇連一晚都連開唔到點撚樣拎出黎賣"},{"pid":"a54f56b0f0874c9fd233b0edacd84cd340246c72","tid":295713,"uid":62841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T11:05:09.000Z","msg":"會頭痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f2d25e52596a53fa55e10b3b60ce696f196eabc","tid":295713,"uid":65361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T11:08:27.000Z","msg":"直吹人會入風之餘<br />\n你訓八個鐘內不自覺吹到你體溫變低就病<br />\n應該開最大吹住幅牆/擺兩部風扇 一部門口一部對面 做對流風減低室溫<br />\n個頭入風老左真係好痛苦"},{"pid":"61451c4f595ee8de15ce36b121910cb102c1317b","tid":295713,"uid":34395,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T11:11:41.000Z","msg":"唔可以吹成晚，因為太熱訓唔到，轉開冷氣成晚啦"},{"pid":"6930ca6cbcbc6a85efd0c1c83f7b836682ca951a","tid":295713,"uid":4548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T11:13:00.000Z","msg":"開冷氣同風扇成晚 第二朝就狂流鼻水。持續三日就會病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家都係瞓前開冷氣整涼間房，瞓就熄 再開返窗"},{"pid":"20ab08d7dde3d658f292b89560888bbb66d21acd","tid":295713,"uid":21309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T11:40:28.000Z","msg":"咁撚驚咩電器都唔好撚用 你手上部電話用得耐都會爆炸架"},{"pid":"ce6a82e824ee72fc9758583da8b9cd9b2ecf35c5","tid":295713,"uid":122812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T12:12:16.000Z","msg":"唔好關晒窗關晒門開風扇，室溫會越黎越熱，因為摩打發熱<br />\n風扇理論上係可以長開永遠唔熄，不過唔好直吹人太耐，撞一撞牆會好d，但係呢個動作會將人造漩渦風變做自然風"},{"pid":"5e9cfd8a349f3f6c00cffebec7fb8a9c72eb