mal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n韓國好似試過死過人<br />\n不過之後有專家解釋番係好巧合先會發生既意外</blockquote><br />\n個阿叔發現懷疑有心血管疾病"},{"pid":"f5744799e27e8f72a533c53d3a7258163d1a5e3d","tid":295713,"uid":104088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T12:44:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4d5c02101feb73cff97542ee1cf30d7fe68db18b","tid":295713,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:04:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吹住個頭, 向住個鼻既話<br />\n會好容易吸唔到氣<br />\nd 空氣吹住, 呼唔到氣<br />\n慢慢抖唔到氣咁就死左<br />\n<br />\n自己都試過訓著左發覺突然好難抖氣<br />\n<br />\n另外都聽過老人家講差d 咁就死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你身體差成咁落街跑多d步吧，連呼吸都困難"},{"pid":"59f39aea6e55d7a156774d1712e37a42598e4cb5","tid":295713,"uid":9769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:07:58.000Z","msg":"中國人香港人不思進取，對住科學問題唔去考究，而係聽呀邊個邊個講，同無知婦孺一樣咁白痴。<br />\n<br />\n人蠢無藥醫，人蠢係天生，蠢人永遠唔會變聰明！"},{"pid":"c9b3e8cc0e16c86dc092401005fe0745b1c82a9e","tid":295713,"uid":17425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:08:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我d親戚 老母 成日話唔好定住吹成晚 就算轉住吹成晚都唔好 <br />\n叫我最好起身熄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n天氣熱吹住先訓到 差唔多訓著又要熄左佢 咁咪本末倒置<br />\n就算你話有得較時間制 你訓到半夜個人熱都熱醒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你地係咪成日都比人咁樣話</blockquote><br />\n但係冷氣又得喎"},{"pid":"dc8e4241a75d26b12460e2e606dfcce8919a7826","tid":295713,"uid":69761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:08:57.000Z","msg":"飯唔可以日日食，涼唔可以日日沖"},{"pid":"56adfd71d4a8ab55968473e5746ad7898d6aeb2f","tid":295713,"uid":104088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:10:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4d732b296e034eb03a82406a66843604403f9518","tid":295713,"uid":104088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:10:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"69a1cd31d30d0bea64407835b79a85f33e573a33","tid":295713,"uid":1259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:12:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>摩打長轉會過熱<br />\n驚一鑊熟</blockquote><br />\n冷氣分體機indoor unit咪一樣有摩打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,<br />\noutdoor unit 壓縮機咪一樣有摩打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,<br />\n咪一樣開足咁耐都無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\noutdoor unit舊野對住街咪重熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"986566dcdcc8046fcde83491c5c3dfebfe73d460","tid":295713,"uid":64092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:12:43.000Z","msg":"會比風扇吹到病嘅根本唔撚識用<br />\n邊個叫你直吹住肚/頭<br />\n<br />\n晚晚開風扇 涼到冷氣都唔洗開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b0bc7d0012920435b1282d2b3f1ade83a8ac7ef","tid":295713,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:13:03.000Z","msg":"唔好吹個人黎訓<br />\n第二朝好易感冒"},{"pid":"c93cca2e7b3546970e17e73ff68ae0671426d8f9","tid":295713,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:14:13.0